Central configuration for qubes-salt-config.

Qubes dom0 does not reliably load custom Salt *pillar* (a plain top.sls in a
pillar_root does not register with Qubes' topd/_tops mechanism and can even
break pillar loading entirely). So — like qusal — this project does NOT use
pillar. All user configuration lives here and is imported by states:

    {% from 'config.jinja' import cfg with context %}
    {{ cfg.qvm.debian.version }}
    {{ cfg.mirror.enabled }}

Edit the values below to customise your environment. This file is deployed to
/srv/salt/slchris/config.jinja and read directly (no pillar, no top.sls).
-#}

